graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator<br/>DSPO]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    DSPO -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes/OpenShift 4.11+]
    DSPO -->|workflow execution| Argo[Argo Workflows<br/>Embedded namespace-scoped]
    DSPO -->|metadata persistence| DB[MariaDB 10.3+<br/>or External MySQL]
    DSPO -->|artifact storage| Storage[S3-compatible Storage<br/>Minio or External S3/AWS]

    %% Optional External Dependencies
    DSPO -.->|optional TLS mgmt| CertMgr[cert-manager<br/>Optional]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|deployment mgmt| ODHOp[ODH Operator]
    DSPO -->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    DSPO -->|pipeline submission| Workbenches[Workbenches<br/>Notebooks]
    DSPO -->|metrics collection| Monitoring[OpenShift Monitoring<br/>Prometheus]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|pipeline UI| DSPO
    Workbenches -->|KFP SDK API| DSPO
    Monitoring -->|ServiceMonitor| DSPO

    %% External Services (Production)
    DSPO -->|production DB| ExtDB[External MySQL/MariaDB]
    DSPO -->|production storage| ExtS3[External S3 Storage<br/>AWS/Compatible]
    DSPO -->|container images| Registry[Image Registries]

    %% Platform Dependencies
    K8s -->|RBAC| DSPO
    K8s -->|CRDs| DSPO
    K8s -->|Routes| OpenShift[OpenShift Routes<br/>Ingress]

    %% Component Relationships
    DSPO -->|creates| DSPA[DataSciencePipelinesApplication<br/>CRD instances]
    DSPA -->|creates| APIServer[DS Pipeline API Server<br/>KFP v2]
    DSPA -->|creates| PersAgent[Persistence Agent]
    DSPA -->|creates| Scheduler[Scheduled Workflow Controller]
    DSPA -->|creates| ArgoCtrl[Argo Workflow Controller]
    DSPA -.->|optional| MLMD[ML Metadata gRPC<br/>+ Envoy Proxy]
    DSPA -.->|optional dev/test| DevStorage[MariaDB + Minio<br/>Dev/Test Only]

    %% Workflow Execution
    ArgoCtrl -->|creates| WorkflowPods[Argo Workflow Pods<br/>Pipeline Tasks]
    WorkflowPods -->|artifacts| Storage
    WorkflowPods -->|artifacts| ExtS3
    WorkflowPods -.->|lineage| MLMD

    %% Downstream Consumers
    KServe[KServe] -.->|model deployment| DSPO
    Elyra[Elyra] -.->|visual pipelines| DSPO

